  <item><title>Version 2026.4.5</title><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 18:20:19 +0000</pubDate><sparkle:version>2026041603</sparkle:version><sparkle:shortVersionString>2026.4.5</sparkle:shortVersionString><sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion><description><![CDATA[<h4>Fixed</h4>
<ul>
<li>Sparkle rejected updates with "improperly signed and could not be</li>
</ul>
<p>validated" because `zip -r` dereferenced symlinks inside the bundle,</p>
<p>breaking the Python.framework / Sparkle.framework layouts and thus</p>
<p>the Apple Code Signature. `build.sh` now zips with `-y` to preserve</p>
<p>symlinks, and the extracted bundle passes `codesign --verify`.</p>]]></description><enclosure url="https://github.com/Y1-Digital/yade-releases/releases/download/v2026.4.5/Yade-2026.4.5.zip" sparkle:edSignature="cnK0Kwp/QYacM7XTdSgW7cnQbnV7c9Juwm/w2WJmQ0by24LpIx0xe1oQxSYaRLQezht+p8qeoCCaYd9v4gIcCQ==" length="211386480" type="application/octet-stream" /></item><item><title>Version 2026.4.4</title><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 18:05:51 +0000</pubDate><sparkle:version>2026041602</sparkle:version><sparkle:shortVersionString>2026.4.4</sparkle:shortVersionString><sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion><description><![CDATA[<h4>Fixed</h4>
<ul>
<li>App launch crashed with `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named</li>
</ul>
<p>'ApplicationServices'` because py2app did not include the framework</p>
<p>in the bundle. Added `pyobjc-framework-ApplicationServices` to</p>
<p>requirements and `ApplicationServices` to setup.py packages.</p>]]></description><enclosure url="https://github.com/Y1-Digital/yade-releases/releases/download/v2026.4.4/Yade-2026.4.4.zip" sparkle:edSignature="KoIQ8ewIO80CYZgaiuIN4xig5bUCCkTPKnlAmtwddqHi9x3tyvA4ie2J7sBbNaDvWuOzenWAO/Swq+Njl3pFAQ==" length="221766959" type="application/octet-stream" /></item><item><title>Version 2026.4.3</title><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 17:48:44 +0000</pubDate><sparkle:version>2026041601</sparkle:version><sparkle:shortVersionString>2026.4.3</sparkle:shortVersionString><sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion><description><![CDATA[<h4>Added</h4>
<ul>
